1
00:00:00,550 --> 00:00:02,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You...</font>

2
00:00:02,670 --> 00:00:08,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I finally found you, Lycanthrope.</font>

3
00:00:12,610 --> 00:00:14,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So it <i>is</i> you.</font>

4
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:20,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the one looking for me.</font>

5
00:00:21,470 --> 00:00:23,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you already know, 
that makes things simple.</font>

6
00:00:23,910 --> 00:00:27,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll pay for what you 
did to our brothers!</font>

7
00:00:28,650 --> 00:00:30,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Najak!</font>

8
00:00:32,680 --> 00:00:35,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't recommend trying to fight me.</font>

9
00:00:36,220 --> 00:00:40,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Many of your friends are still 
trapped at the moon altar.</font>

10
00:00:41,100 --> 00:00:43,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you care what happens to them?</font>

11
00:00:44,500 --> 00:00:47,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell us one thing. What do you want?</font>

12
00:00:48,690 --> 00:00:54,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To become this nation's—no, 
this world's king.</font>

13
00:01:00,660 --> 00:01:04,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And to do that, I need your blood.</font>

14
00:01:05,550 --> 00:01:07,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come with me.</font>

15
00:01:10,210 --> 00:01:11,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry.</font>

16
00:01:12,070 --> 00:01:20,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I become king, I'll allow you 
werewolves to serve me alongside vampires.</font>

17
00:01:20,150 --> 00:01:21,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Screw you!</font>

18
00:01:23,330 --> 00:01:24,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go with you.</font>

19
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:29,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In exchange, promise you 
won't hurt my brothers.</font>

20
00:01:30,070 --> 00:01:32,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Very well.</font>

21
00:01:35,670 --> 00:01:38,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. I'll do as you say.</font>

22
00:01:38,320 --> 00:01:39,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Khan!</font>

23
00:01:39,590 --> 00:01:40,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't do it!</font>

24
00:01:40,570 --> 00:01:41,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Khan!</font>

25
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:42,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You still can't—</font>

26
00:01:45,110 --> 00:01:47,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be fine.</font>

27
00:01:50,010 --> 00:01:52,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care of Najak.</font>

28
00:02:06,870 --> 00:02:09,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shall we go?</font>

29
00:02:12,440 --> 00:02:15,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Someone you've been wanting 
to see is there, too.</font>

30
00:03:55,060 --> 00:04:00,970
<font face="Times New Roman" size="13"><b>{\an8}<font size="30">- Dark Moon: The Blood Altar -</font></b></font>

31
00:04:02,990 --> 00:04:05,970
<font face="Times New Roman" size="23" color="#f9fcfd"><b><font size="22">- Vargr's Blood -</font></b></font>

32
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:20,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shion, are you okay?</font>

33
00:04:21,690 --> 00:04:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine.</font>

34
00:04:23,210 --> 00:04:25,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha will heal us again, right?</font>

35
00:04:26,650 --> 00:04:31,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, I think our 
healing is slowing down.</font>

36
00:04:32,250 --> 00:04:35,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My grip feels weak.</font>

37
00:04:35,610 --> 00:04:37,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So does mine.</font>

38
00:04:38,390 --> 00:04:41,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did something happen to Sooha?</font>

39
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's hurry.</font>

40
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:46,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something's coming.</font>

41
00:04:56,200 --> 00:04:58,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing here?</font>

42
00:04:58,250 --> 00:04:59,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are <i>you</i> doing here?</font>

43
00:05:02,770 --> 00:05:04,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dardan took Khan?!</font>

44
00:05:06,850 --> 00:05:08,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're running out of time.</font>

45
00:05:09,010 --> 00:05:10,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once the full moon rises...</font>

46
00:05:10,710 --> 00:05:12,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'll take her power.</font>

47
00:05:12,300 --> 00:05:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do we not stand a chance?</font>

48
00:05:14,290 --> 00:05:16,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not letting that happen!</font>

49
00:05:17,170 --> 00:05:21,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Either way, I can't believe 
Sooha is a princess.</font>

50
00:05:38,130 --> 00:05:39,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha!</font>

51
00:05:43,390 --> 00:05:45,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She gave them too much power.</i></font>

52
00:05:47,060 --> 00:05:50,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her name is Princess Selen. 
Haven't you missed her?</font>

53
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess Selen?</font>

54
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:54,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right. You don't know.</font>

55
00:05:54,950 --> 00:05:57,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, I'll enlighten you.</font>

56
00:06:00,330 --> 00:06:03,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's the reincarnation of 
an ancient kingdom's princess?</font>

57
00:06:05,050 --> 00:06:07,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You must've noticed it, too.</font>

58
00:06:07,590 --> 00:06:10,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha has the power to control us.</font>

59
00:06:10,840 --> 00:06:12,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, guys!</font>

60
00:06:16,670 --> 00:06:21,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We also instinctively want to protect her.</font>

61
00:06:21,440 --> 00:06:22,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

62
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:26,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, were you guys reincarnated like her?</font>

63
00:06:26,780 --> 00:06:29,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, in our case...</font>

64
00:06:30,060 --> 00:06:33,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess Selen used her dying breath</font>

65
00:06:33,660 --> 00:06:38,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to send our souls centuries 
into the future and save us.</font>

66
00:06:42,750 --> 00:06:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'd forgotten for hundreds of years and 
hid that we were vampires until now.</font>

67
00:06:54,890 --> 00:06:59,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We didn't even know why we existed.</font>

68
00:07:00,390 --> 00:07:03,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the princess was reborn as Sooha.</font>

69
00:07:03,980 --> 00:07:07,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meeting her brought back 
our past memories.</font>

70
00:07:08,230 --> 00:07:12,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of everything that happened 
when the kingdom fell.</font>

71
00:07:13,470 --> 00:07:17,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that we exist to protect Sooha.</font>

72
00:07:17,740 --> 00:07:21,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The time has come to settle 
matters with Dardan.</font>

73
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This time, we'll stop him.</font>

74
00:07:23,710 --> 00:07:24,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

75
00:07:27,890 --> 00:07:29,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha...</font>

76
00:07:30,010 --> 00:07:34,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, give me your blood.</font>

77
00:07:38,690 --> 00:07:40,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give it to me, or else...</font>

78
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:46,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm worried.</font>

79
00:07:46,810 --> 00:07:51,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Khan still hasn't transformed 
into a wolf a single time.</font>

80
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:40,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the power of Vargr's blood.</font>

81
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:41,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sooha! Are you okay?</font>

82
00:08:42,130 --> 00:08:43,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wake up!</font>

83
00:08:43,340 --> 00:08:46,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who said you could 
lay hands on the princess?</font>

84
00:08:54,230 --> 00:08:56,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You bastard! What did you do to Sooha?!</font>

85
00:08:56,700 --> 00:09:03,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you, your brothers' lives
 depend on your cooperation.</font>

86
00:09:07,180 --> 00:09:14,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As a Lycanthrope, you won't sit 
back and watch your brothers die.</font>

87
00:09:14,030 --> 00:09:15,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I wrong?</font>

88
00:09:16,920 --> 00:09:19,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get away from the princess.</font>

89
00:09:25,210 --> 00:09:29,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you hear me?!</font>

90
00:09:33,210 --> 00:09:36,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've also fallen for her,
 haven't you?</font>

91
00:09:36,770 --> 00:09:41,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you should be willing to 
sacrifice your brothers to save her!</font>

92
00:09:42,080 --> 00:09:48,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't save either 
because you can't choose!</font>

93
00:10:03,740 --> 00:10:04,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sun...</font>

94
00:10:06,060 --> 00:10:10,020
<font face="Times New Roman" size="13"><b>{\an8}- Dark Moon: The Blood Altar -</b></font>

95
00:10:10,060 --> 00:10:14,000
<font face="Times New Roman" size="13"><b>{\an8}- Dark Moon: The Blood Altar -</b></font>

96
00:10:23,510 --> 00:10:27,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now I have everything I need.</font>

97
00:10:27,870 --> 00:10:29,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The incantation.</font>

98
00:10:29,660 --> 00:10:30,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The princess.</font>

99
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The blood of Vargr.</font>

100
00:10:37,650 --> 00:10:45,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When the full moon rises high in the 
night sky, I will recite the incantation.</font>

101
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:51,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The power sealed within the altar will be 
released and passed on to the princess.</font>

102
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:58,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I will claim that power for myself.</font>

103
00:11:04,060 --> 00:11:08,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If only I were stronger...</i></font>

104
00:11:12,040 --> 00:11:14,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Lycanthrope.</i></font>

105
00:11:15,780 --> 00:11:18,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Lycanthrope.</i></font>

106
00:11:19,010 --> 00:11:20,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That voice...</font>

107
00:11:26,300 --> 00:11:28,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lycanthrope.</font>

108
00:11:32,350 --> 00:11:38,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Within your veins courses my blood. 
The blood of Vargr, the wolf god.</font>

109
00:11:39,640 --> 00:11:44,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To our kind, you are like the moon.</font>

110
00:11:44,650 --> 00:11:48,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can awaken their strength.</font>

111
00:11:48,210 --> 00:11:51,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But how?</font>

112
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:55,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your instincts will show you the way.</font>

113
00:11:56,420 --> 00:12:01,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Call out to the others 
and become our moon.</font>

114
00:12:01,780 --> 00:12:06,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Use your power to protect 
the princess you serve.</font>

115
00:12:27,940 --> 00:12:32,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I carry Vargr's blood.</font>

116
00:12:47,490 --> 00:12:50,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a Lycanthrope!</font>

117
00:12:53,000 --> 00:12:55,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a Lycanthrope!</font>

118
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:57,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's here to save us!</font>

119
00:13:08,110 --> 00:13:09,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run, guys!</font>

120
00:13:09,850 --> 00:13:10,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry!</font>

121
00:13:19,270 --> 00:13:21,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're wasting your time!</font>

122
00:13:34,370 --> 00:13:37,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You told me not to touch 
the princess, right?</font>

123
00:13:37,860 --> 00:13:41,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, right back at you!</font>

124
00:13:41,880 --> 00:13:44,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't let you have your way!</font>

125
00:13:46,970 --> 00:13:48,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Silence!</font>

126
00:13:55,980 --> 00:14:00,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're just a werewolf. 
You think you can beat me now?</font>

127
00:14:01,290 --> 00:14:07,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you defy me, I'll kill you.
 You and your brothers.</font>

128
00:14:16,410 --> 00:14:17,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that?</font>

129
00:14:17,950 --> 00:14:19,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sounds like a lot of them.</font>

130
00:14:27,710 --> 00:14:29,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're not enemies.</font>

131
00:14:29,840 --> 00:14:31,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're our kind.</font>

132
00:14:37,990 --> 00:14:40,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened? Where did you come from?</font>

133
00:14:40,060 --> 00:14:43,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The moon altar.</font>

134
00:14:44,110 --> 00:14:45,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's Khan?</font>

135
00:14:45,180 --> 00:14:46,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is he all right?</font>

136
00:14:46,150 --> 00:14:52,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Khan? You mean that Lycanthrope?</font>

137
00:14:53,320 --> 00:14:56,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He saved us.</font>

138
00:14:58,150 --> 00:14:59,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then Khan...</font>

139
00:14:59,450 --> 00:15:01,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">...transformed into a wolf!</font>

140
00:15:05,330 --> 00:15:07,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, where's Khan?</font>

141
00:15:07,260 --> 00:15:11,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's facing Dardan all by himself.</font>

142
00:15:21,850 --> 00:15:24,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay there.</font>

143
00:15:39,870 --> 00:15:43,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The seal has begun to release.</font>

144
00:15:44,370 --> 00:15:49,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the power passed down for 
generations in the ancient kingdom.</font>

145
00:15:51,130 --> 00:15:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can feel its tremendous energy 
just by standing near it.</font>

146
00:15:55,920 --> 00:15:57,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Such overwhelming power!</font>

147
00:15:58,530 --> 00:16:02,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And this will all be mine.</font>

148
00:16:04,730 --> 00:16:06,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess.</font>

149
00:16:06,820 --> 00:16:08,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's begin.</font>

150
00:16:35,880 --> 00:16:36,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look!</font>

151
00:16:36,820 --> 00:16:39,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That light... Is that...</font>

152
00:16:40,560 --> 00:16:44,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The royal power sealed in the altar...</font>

153
00:16:44,690 --> 00:16:47,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The ritual must've started.</font>

154
00:16:47,020 --> 00:16:47,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go!</font>

155
00:16:48,490 --> 00:16:55,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This power will be all mine.</font>

156
00:17:01,790 --> 00:17:04,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't let you have it.</font>

157
00:17:12,120 --> 00:17:13,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop!</font>

158
00:17:17,020 --> 00:17:18,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mutt!</font>

159
00:17:23,810 --> 00:17:28,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't allow you to live any longer!</font>

160
00:17:36,550 --> 00:17:37,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go!</font>

161
00:17:40,240 --> 00:17:42,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Khan, are you okay?!</font>

162
00:17:49,170 --> 00:17:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heli...</font>

163
00:17:51,510 --> 00:17:53,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're too late.</font>

164
00:17:53,670 --> 00:17:55,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did you even bother coming?</font>

165
00:17:57,190 --> 00:17:58,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sooha.</i></font>

166
00:18:00,110 --> 00:18:02,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Her hair color... Could it be...</i></font>

167
00:18:02,600 --> 00:18:03,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Khan!</font>

168
00:18:03,740 --> 00:18:04,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Khan!</font>

169
00:18:05,030 --> 00:18:06,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's badly injured.</font>

170
00:18:06,730 --> 00:18:08,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang in there!</font>

171
00:18:10,970 --> 00:18:13,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine.</font>

172
00:18:13,220 --> 00:18:14,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are our brothers?</font>

173
00:18:16,120 --> 00:18:17,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're all safe.</font>

174
00:18:17,730 --> 00:18:19,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... I see.</font>

175
00:18:29,030 --> 00:18:31,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is it because she granted us power?</i></font>

176
00:18:38,250 --> 00:18:40,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, this is...</i></font>

177
00:18:41,750 --> 00:18:43,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Our power...</font>

178
00:18:43,740 --> 00:18:48,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's being drained from our bodies.</font>

179
00:18:51,390 --> 00:18:56,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The power Sooha shared with 
us is returning to her.</i></font>

180
00:18:57,030 --> 00:18:58,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is bad!</font>

181
00:18:58,180 --> 00:18:59,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have to stop him, now!</font>

182
00:18:59,980 --> 00:19:03,170
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>Jakah, I'm going to draw 
Dardan's attention.</i></font>

183
00:19:03,170 --> 00:19:04,840
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24" color="#f4e1e1"><i>While he's distracted, save Sooha.</i></font>

184
00:19:08,660 --> 00:19:11,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My telepathy's not working.</font>

185
00:19:11,640 --> 00:19:13,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jakah, get Sooha!</font>

186
00:19:17,690 --> 00:19:20,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't use my power?!</i></font>

187
00:19:21,140 --> 00:19:23,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the best part.</font>

188
00:19:23,890 --> 00:19:26,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mustn't interfere 
with Lord Dardan's plans!</font>

189
00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:04,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watch as everything becomes mine.</font>

190
00:20:04,760 --> 00:20:09,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Both this power and 
the princess belong to me.</font>

191
00:20:09,890 --> 00:20:12,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sear this sight into your eyes!</font>

192
00:20:17,060 --> 00:20:19,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go, guys!</font>

193
00:20:19,010 --> 00:20:19,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

194
00:20:33,310 --> 00:20:35,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let us handle this!</font>

195
00:20:35,120 --> 00:20:36,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go defeat Dardan!</font>

196
00:20:43,130 --> 00:20:44,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dardan!</font>

197
00:20:45,630 --> 00:20:49,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't stand a chance against me.</font>

198
00:20:59,690 --> 00:21:02,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How laughable.</font>

199
00:21:02,030 --> 00:21:05,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were once the kingdom's 
greatest knights.</font>

200
00:21:06,410 --> 00:21:11,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And now you're kneeling at my feet.</font>

201
00:21:12,500 --> 00:21:16,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soon, you'll lose all your power.</font>

202
00:21:18,580 --> 00:21:27,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once you lose the power you were granted, 
you'll realize you're nothing at all.</font>

203
00:23:34,170 --> 00:23:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Next time, Episode 12: 
"Dark Moon: The Moon Altar."</i></font>

204
00:23:37,030 --> 00:23:40,250
<font face="Times New Roman" size="23" color="#f9fcfd"><b><font size="22">- The Moon Altar -</font></b></font>

